 [^1] have smoked us out.  So last night when it started I was going to send for fire company.  Was John mad if I had been alone (I) would have done it.  The Shermans came in - they said it was not wood odor.  Oh it was awful, I think she does it on purposes.  I called Middelton *(landlord, perhaps?...ed)* and said if it did not stop we would move (Where?)  Jim Loughlin was over the other night... |
